reviewText: Great season, but got a refund because one of the discs didn't work. Other than that, I would have given this purchase 5 stars.
When I purchased this; most of the discs were scratched and the DVD case was partially broken. I recommend you not to order anything outside the country unless you really want it.
The best show on television. Great actors and writers. Can not predict what is going to happen next. I hope there is some way it can continue for a long time.
